---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Web Design Services in Ahmedabad | DC technolabs"
  description="Professional web design services in Ahmedabad. Custom, responsive websites that engage visitors and drive conversions. Get a free quote today!"
>
  <Header />
  
  <div style="height: 80px;"></div>
  
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Web Design Services in Ahmedabad</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Beautiful, user-friendly designs that convert visitors into customers</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-wrapper">
      <div class="main-content">
        <h2>Transform Your Online Presence with Professional Web Design</h2>
        <p>Your website is often the first impression potential customers have of your business. At DC technolabs, we create stunning, modern websites that not only look great but are strategically designed to convert visitors into customers.</p>
        
        <p>Based in Ahmedabad, we understand the local market and create designs that resonate with your target audience while maintaining international quality standards.</p>
        
        <h3>What's Included in Our Web Design Service</h3>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li><strong>Custom Responsive Design:</strong> Your website will look perfect on all devices - desktop, tablet, and mobile</li>
          <li><strong>User Experience (UX) Optimization:</strong> Intuitive navigation and layouts that guide visitors to take action</li>
          <li><strong>Brand-Aligned Visual Identity:</strong> Colors, fonts, and imagery that reflect your brand personality</li>
          <li><strong>Interactive Elements:</strong> Engaging animations and micro-interactions that delight users</li>
          <li><strong>Mobile-First Approach:</strong> Designed for the way modern users browse on their phones</li>
          <li><strong>Fast Loading Times:</strong> Optimized images and code for lightning-fast performance</li>
          <li><strong>Conversion-Focused Design:</strong> Strategic placement of CTAs and trust signals</li>
          <li><strong>SEO-Friendly Structure:</strong> Built with search engines in mind from day one</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Our Web Design Process</h3>
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">01</div>
            <h4>Discovery & Research</h4>
            <p>We learn about your business, goals, target audience, and competitors</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">02</div>
            <h4>Strategy & Planning</h4>
            <p>Create sitemap, wireframes, and design strategy aligned with your goals</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">03</div>
            <h4>Design Creation</h4>
            <p>Develop visual designs with your brand colors, fonts, and imagery</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">04</div>
            <h4>Review & Refinement</h4>
            <p>You review designs, provide feedback, and we refine until perfect</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">05</div>
            <h4>Development & Launch</h4>
            <p>Convert designs to code, test thoroughly, and launch your site</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Common Problems We Solve</h3>
        <ul class="problems-list">
          <li>Outdated website that doesn't reflect your current business</li>
          <li>Poor mobile experience driving away potential customers</li>
          <li>Confusing navigation that makes it hard to find information</li>
          <li>Slow loading times affecting your Google rankings</li>
          <li>Generic template design that looks like everyone else</li>
          <li>Low conversion rates despite getting decent traffic</li>
          <li>Unprofessional appearance hurting your brand credibility</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Why Choose DC technolabs for Web Design?</h3>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li><strong>Local Expertise:</strong> We understand Ahmedabad market and audience preferences</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Solutions:</strong> No cookie-cutter templates - every design is unique to your business</li>
          <li><strong>Conversion Focus:</strong> We design to achieve your business goals, not just look pretty</li>
          <li><strong>Fast Turnaround:</strong> Most projects completed in 2-4 weeks</li>
          <li><strong>Transparent Pricing:</strong> Clear quotes with no hidden fees</li>
          <li><strong>Ongoing Support:</strong> We're here to help even after launch</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Pricing & Packages</h3>
        <p>Our web design services start from ₹25,000 for small business websites. Enterprise solutions are custom-quoted based on your specific requirements.</p>
        
        <div class="packages-grid">
          <div class="package-card">
            <h4>Starter Package</h4>
            <p class="price">Starting at ₹25,000</p>
            <ul>
              <li>5-page responsive website</li>
              <li>Mobile-optimized design</li>
              <li>Contact form integration</li>
              <li>Social media links</li>
              <li>2 rounds of revisions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="package-card featured">
            <div class="badge">Most Popular</div>
            <h4>Professional Package</h4>
            <p class="price">Starting at ₹50,000</p>
            <ul>
              <li>10-page responsive website</li>
              <li>Custom design & branding</li>
              <li>Advanced animations</li>
              <li>SEO optimization</li>
              <li>Google Analytics setup</li>
              <li>3 rounds of revisions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="package-card">
            <h4>Enterprise Package</h4>
            <p class="price">Custom Quote</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Unlimited pages</li>
              <li>Advanced functionality</li>
              <li>Custom integrations</li>
              <li>Priority support</li>
              <li>Dedicated project manager</li>
              <li>Unlimited revisions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <div class="faq">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>How long does it take to design a website?</h4>
            <p>Most small to medium websites take 2-4 weeks from start to launch. Larger projects may take 6-8 weeks depending on complexity.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Will my website work on mobile phones?</h4>
            <p>Absolutely! All our designs are mobile-responsive and tested on various devices to ensure perfect functionality.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Can I update the website myself after launch?</h4>
            <p>Yes! We can build your site on a CMS like WordPress, making it easy for you to update content without coding knowledge.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Do you provide website hosting?</h4>
            <p>We can recommend reliable hosting providers and help with setup. We also offer managed hosting as an add-on service.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>What if I don't like the initial design?</h4>
            <p>We include multiple revision rounds in all packages. We work with you until you're completely satisfied with the design.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Do you redesign existing websites?</h4>
            <p>Yes! We specialize in website redesigns and can modernize your existing site while preserving your SEO rankings.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Will my website be SEO-friendly?</h4>
            <p>Yes, we build all websites with SEO best practices including proper heading structure, fast loading, and mobile optimization.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Can you integrate third-party tools and services?</h4>
            <p>Absolutely! We can integrate payment gateways, CRM systems, email marketing tools, and more.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>What areas in Ahmedabad do you serve?</h4>
            <p>We serve all areas of Ahmedabad including Satellite, Vastrapur, SG Highway, Bodakdev, Prahlad Nagar, and surrounding areas.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Do you provide maintenance after launch?</h4>
            <p>Yes! We offer ongoing maintenance packages to keep your website secure, updated, and running smoothly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="cta-box">
          <h3>Ready to Get Started?</h3>
          <p>Get a free consultation and custom quote for your web design project</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:+919662608986" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Call +91 96626-08986</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Quick Contact</h3>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong><br><a href="tel:+919662608986">+91 96626-08986</a></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong><br><a href="mailto:hello@dctechnolabs.com">hello@dctechnolabs.com</a></p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem;">Get Free Quote</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Other Services</h3>
          <ul class="service-links">
            <li><a href="/services/web-development">Web Development</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/seo">SEO Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/ppc">PPC Management</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Service Areas</h3>
          <p>Proudly serving businesses across:</p>
          <ul class="area-links">
            <li><a href="/locations/ahmedabad">Ahmedabad</a></li>
            <li><a href="/locations/gandhinagar">Gandhinagar</a></li>
            <li><a href="/locations/surat">Surat</a></li>
            <li><a href="/locations/vadodara">Vadodara</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, var(--secondary-light) 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-hero h1 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .content-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  
  .main-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .main-content h3 {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .main-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .feature-list,
  .problems-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .feature-list li,
  .problems-list li {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  
  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .problems-list li::before {
    content: '✗';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #ef4444;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  
  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .step h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .step p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .packages-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }
  
  .package-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .package-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
  }
  
  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: 20px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .package-card h4 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .price {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .package-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .package-card li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  
  .package-card li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .package-card li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  
  .faq {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .faq-item {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  
  .faq-item h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .faq-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }
  
  .cta-box h3 {
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }
  
  .cta-box p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }
  
  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .sidebar-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .sidebar-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .sidebar-card a {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .service-links,
  .area-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
  }
  
  .service-links li,
  .area-links li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  
  .service-links li:last-child,
  .area-links li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .service-links a,
  .area-links a {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .service-links a:hover,
  .area-links a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .content-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
    
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .cta-buttons .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
